review:
*** ** *** **** ****** * **** *** **** **** Your half of the issues are solved when speaks to you.  Very humble, patience and loving. She greets every patient with a smile which is very good quality.
**** ***** ** *** ********* ***** ***** I was suffering from irregular periods and seen many gynaecologist but it was Dr Shinde who actually helped my period to get regularized. Im a satisfied patient. I recommend her to all the females. She's a doctor who believes in less medications.
Thank you Doctor and Practo :)

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: Absolutely wonderful she is. Soooo positive and radiant. Half my worries flew away just by looking at her. And she was verrrry veryyyyy nice and quick to figure out what the problem was. And gave medicines accordingly. Also helped by talking about how I should get some nutrition advice and physio assistance for a better health. Thank u mam. It felt like meeting a sweet family member. Your smile is infectious. An you are so warm. Thank you. Also the staff at Cloud 9 Malad are just soo very humane and amzing. Smiling ... helpful n efficient. Thank you. Also the customer service girl Saira was extremely amazing and reaaly human. These people must be recognised and more such people should be hired.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,
review: Well I have never come across a doctor like her in my entire life. She is very calm n patient. Good listener n makes you feel its not a big issue fr what you hv cm for. Easy treatment. Encourages her patients to call her if they need to ask anything. She spk to quite a few patients on the ph while examining me. Very few doctors do that and she shared her no on her own without me asking. Poise n elegant. Lots to learn frm her. I came out of her cabin feeling light hearted. N believe me it was not those sweet talks it was genuine.... May God bless her. Would recommend her without any doubt.
reply_text: Thanks.
